<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Farewell Message</title>

<style>

body{
    background-color:#0b0b0b;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    color:white;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    height:100vh;
}

.card{
    background:#1a1a1a;
    padding:40px;
    border-radius:15px;
    width:400px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0px 0px 25px rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
}

.photo{
    width:200px;
    height:200px;
    border-radius:50%;
    object-fit:cover;
    border:4px solid gold;
}

.name{
    font-size:28px;
    margin-top:15px;
    color:gold;
}

.message{
    margin-top:20px;
    font-size:16px;
    line-height:1.6;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<img src="studentphoto.jpg" class="photo">

<div class="name">Student Name</div>

<div class="message">
Thank you for the memories, the laughs, and the moments that made school unforgettable.
Wishing you all the best for the amazing journey ahead!
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
